&lt;h2 id=&#34;阿里云oss服务配置图床&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#阿里云oss服务配置图床&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 阿里云 OSS 服务配置图床&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;注册 阿里云账号&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;搜索 OSS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154657711.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154657711.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154657711&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;点击 立即购买（一般选择基础款购买，按需购买即可）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154602544.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154602544.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154602544&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;购买完成后回到 管理控制台&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154532322.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154532322.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154532322&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在 Bucket 列表 创建 Bucket (其中 地域 选择离自己近的，读写权限 选择 公共读)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154449067.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154449067.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154449067&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;创建 Bucket 后，点击自己创建的 Bucket，新建目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154300771.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154300771.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154300771&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
