&lt;p&gt;头像–&amp;gt;AccessKey–&amp;gt; 新建 AccessKey，复制保存一下&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154143507.png&#34; class=&#34;lazyload placeholder&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://picture1-for-typora.oss-cn-qingdao.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20221023154143507.png&#34; srcset=&#34;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221023154143507&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
